		<Group d:userLabel="层_2" d:type="layer" visible="false">
		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寒涌持者旋转冰锯扔出一枚锯片，造成<span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>伤害，同时近身旋转的锯片也会造成</span><span color="#99ffff">75%</span><span>伤害，两者造成的伤害存在(1,0.5)的衰减。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寒涌持者驱使灵力将飞锯附魔，攻击力提升<span color="#ffbfbf">20%</span><span>，随后产生一次冰雾震，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">60%</span><span>伤害，仅施放一次。<br/>施放后，寒涌持者之后施放的普攻将造成</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>伤害，且第三段普攻将产生向前切的冰锯。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/暝视龙武士%B7寒涌持者.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
