		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/暝视龙武士%B7寒涌持者.assets/Image_17.png')" x="576" y="406" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/暝视龙武士%B7寒涌持者.assets/Image_18.png')" x="576" y="630" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/暝视龙武士%B7寒涌持者.assets/Image_19.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寒涌持者使用飞锯进行纵、横、切至多3段的攻击，分别造成<span color="#b8b8b8">60%,90%,70%</span><span>伤害，第三段留在地上的锯子额外造成多段</span><span color="#b8b8b8">5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
